{"tid":441890,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉］骨微裂增高","createTime":"2017-10-20T05:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T09:29:02.000Z","uid":119290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8115e8416a253fd4f288cf5e5fa64568aab32fb9","tid":441890,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"骨骼被不斷形成和再吸收。當鈣化基質的形成速度快於它被吸收的速度，骨骼得以生長。當骨骼外表面發生基質沉積時，就會發生直徑生長，長骨的骨骺板上發生線性生長。這些板塊是骨骺和骨幹之間的部分，骨骺面的關節軟骨細胞不斷劃分引發骨骼的生長。<br />\n<br />\n人體全身骨骼每天都在新陳代謝，隨着人體新陳代謝的不斷改造，人體全身骨骼每3年都有重新走合一次，人體通過專門的運動從而使新陳代謝加快，達到增高的目的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/ygr3jg.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Fygr3jg.html&d=yxF5I2YAp5zYew9dlCv25C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=dfe7ed80\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/ygr3jg.html</a>"},{"pid":"698bf4b6c993f4dc2b88e5007e495131c77728ad","tid":441890,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"不嬲有"},{"pid":"1ab0ecf7ea567d77115898dccafd8cbcf5bf0b7d","tid":441890,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲有</blockquote><br />\n有冇效？"},{"pid":"7d4a6651b0d2ba8d0748d74ce8b3a313498e9277","tid":441890,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"失敗左會唔會仲矮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246fb984110c8e39d6300a88008e705f5aa57899","tid":441890,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失敗左會唔會仲矮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直接訓棺材"},{"pid":"73d1b0ba479e87aeb44f86b5e95bdcbbbcb96a84","tid":441890,"uid":72991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>失敗左會唔會仲矮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma